cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DL 

The paper proposes a machine learning system, LitGen, that uses deep learning to predict the type of evidence provided by each paper in genetic literature. This involves natural language processing and information retrieval, which are core topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
